{
  "stem": "2735.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "What we were getting was-- yeah, now this guy, the [NON-ENGLISH] was mostly drunk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And he had a girlfriend, probably could be his daughter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And you couldn't find him never.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And to get a order for something to get from them, the villagers only used to go to work because they were wearing like very warm-- make like a-- filled with cotton, like jackets.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And inside they had very big pockets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "So whatever they stole going home, that was the pay for the day because all the threads didn't amount to anything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "I don't know before the war, but during the war, because they had to give away the grain to the army, so they had to go to work, so that's what they used to steal, whatever they could they took down from the fields.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] now the other family didn't have anything to-- she had the child who was-- she couldn't feed him, because she had no milk.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "But he was very cute.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "He lives in Israel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "He was a cute baby.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "And an old woman just was giving milk, and-- but her father had ulcers, and he was really suffering from hunger.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "So he came to the office one time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And he waited for days so that the director would give him an order for some food, for some grain, or for something.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "And finally he found him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "And he gave him the order.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And before he leaves, this young guy says, you-- you need my signature, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "And the director already left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "He gives him the paper, and he tears it to pieces, and then throws it out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "The end was that he was going to beg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "He was a musician.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "He played the violin.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
